# CURSOR RULES FOR ASTRO BLOG PROJECT

## Build & Development
- Build command: `pnpm build`
- Development server: `pnpm dev`
- Format code: `pnpm format`
- Lint code: `pnpm lint`

## Code Style
- Use TypeScript for type safety
- Double quotes for strings
- Semicolons required
- 2-space indentation
- Max line length: 80 characters
- Arrow functions with implicit return when possible
- Use functional components for React
- Follow Astro component patterns (.astro files)
- Use Tailwind for styling

## Cloudflare Deployment
- Prefer pnpm for commands
- Output directory: `dist`
- Compatible with Node.js 18+
- Use `npx wrangler pages deploy dist` for CLI deployment
- Avoid Node-specific APIs incompatible with Cloudflare

## File Structure
- Page components in `src/pages`
- Reusable components in `src/components`
- Layouts in `src/layouts`
- Blog content in `src/content/blog`
- Utils in `src/utils`